reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for toddler fun!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these cars for my son’s 2nd birthday. They come in a plastic case which is nice for storage because let me tell ya, you don’t want to step on these barefoot! I also purchased a car play mat and works great on the carpet. They are different colors, designs, and are labeled which makes for fun play time AND learning. They are a little smaller than matchbox cars so would definitely use with adult supervision. If your child loves cars just as much as mine, you won’t be disappointed.
